    intro: 'The best AI tools for logo design in 2026 are Recraft, Ideogram, Canva AI, and Midjourney. Recraft is the only major AI tool that generates editable SVG vectors natively — essential for logos that need to scale from a favicon to a billboard. Ideogram produces clean, stylised logos with legible text, solving the text-in-image problem that makes other AI tools impractical for wordmarks. Canva AI combines an extensive template library with AI design suggestions and is the fastest path to a polished brand kit for non-designers. Midjourney excels at conceptual logomarks and brand icon generation.',
